{"tid":766870,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人箍牙箍過專科鄭偉昌？","createTime":"2018-08-04T03:54:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-10T18:45:52.000Z","uid":10464,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0e88cc9632d1dc94aad3b571d050148b02037cce","tid":766870,"uid":10464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T03:54:54.000Z","msg":"屋企人叫我去consult下佢<br />\n不過consult完後 我覺得佢麻麻<br />\n因為之前consult過其他專科<br />\n覺得佢冇咁pro 又講得唔詳細<br />\n望兩眼 講幾句就算咁<br />\n仲有佢同我之前幾個醫生講嘅野都唔同<br />\n之前啲醫生都覺得可能要做正顎手術先會靚晒<br />\n啫係都有啲複雜<br />\n佢就好輕鬆咁話好易箍好 唔複雜<br />\n連x ray都未睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有佢都係主張唔用骨釘嘅<br />\n前啲醫生都話過用骨釘效果會好好多<br />\n自己都做過research 的確係咁<br />\n佢嘅價錢喺專科嚟講係幾平 <br />\n我之前睇過嘅普通科仲貴過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知價錢有冇反映質素呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外我都係第一次知專科會包埋洗牙剝牙etc <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時嗰啲都唔包嘅<br />\n唔知係好事定壞事啦<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d419875e4375d06dd2410ac374892f774cb007d","tid":766870,"uid":1400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T04:40:11.000Z","msg":"ching rich"},{"pid":"d9ed3dc94e0165968c6688c73cb81474b977c45a","tid":766870,"uid":10464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d419875e4375d06dd2410ac374892f774cb007d","tid":766870,"uid":1400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T04:40:11.000Z","msg":"ching rich"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T11:06:07.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 好耐冇見"},{"pid":"84c443a85e9ae92a1a825a52a7903d3134d794b2","tid":766870,"uid":35587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T11:35:08.000Z","msg":"ching rich"},{"pid":"c648e7cee31384e7886e6e39d3947b46a18758fb","tid":766870,"uid":12823,"like":0,"dislike":0,